### Project Nomad API - REST Client Test File
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1

### ============================================
### Health & Info
### ============================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/info

###

### Public Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/config

### ============================================
### Models
### ============================================

### List All Models
GET {{baseUrl}}/models

###

### Create a FireSTARR Model
# @name createFirestarr
POST {{baseUrl}}/models
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test FireSTARR Model",
  "engineType": "firestarr"
}

###

### Create a WISE Model
# @name createWise
POST {{baseUrl}}/models
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test WISE Model",
  "engineType": "wise"
}

###

### Get Model by ID (use id from create response)
@modelId = {{createFirestarr.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/models/{{modelId}}

###

### Execute Model (returns jobId)
# @name executeModel
POST {{baseUrl}}/models/{{modelId}}/execute

### ============================================
### Jobs
### ============================================

### List All Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs

###

### List Pending Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?status=pending

###

### List Running Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?status=running

###

### Get Job Status (use jobId from execute response)
@jobId = {{executeModel.response.body.jobId}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}

###

### Cancel Job
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}

